{"tid":2122562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「禁足令」謠言係為「健康碼」做既期望管理","createTime":"2020-07-24T05:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T06:52:37.000Z","uid":88743,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f45b16464f4eb8271e547cd28836344dbc046f8c","tid":2122562,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:16:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/21/P2020072100609.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202007%2F21%2FP2020072100609.htm&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6CrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=81439f10\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/21/P2020072100609.htm</a><br />\n政府澄清「禁足令」謠言<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  對於有謠言指因應2019冠狀病毒病疫情，政府可能在未來數天實施所謂「禁足令」，政府發言人今日（七月二十一日）澄清絕無其事。<br />\n<br />\n  發言人說：「疫情嚴峻，我們應該齊心抗疫。市民千萬不要被虛假消息誤導，更不應發放或散播謠言，引起不必要的恐慌。」<br />\n<br />\n  發言人呼籲市民應繼續遵守社交距離的指引，減少外出，同時保持個人和環境衞生。市民亦應留意政府公布有關2019冠狀病毒病的最新消息。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年7月21日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間18時08分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n實施「健康碼」時，班撚屌廢老應該會咁講：<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"violet\">政府唔實施最嚴既「禁足令」<br />\n只係實施「健康碼」<br />\n好彩咋，仲可以出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"634591a9e5103f74732ddcd85c0f1a30027f38c1","tid":2122562,"uid":210190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"仲要可以全民支持DNA送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5212b19623f8c3048d73582707a2213c2ff030d6","tid":2122562,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:36:28.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp瘋傳政府設禁足令《香港01》嚴正澄清：無發布相關消息<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2122662\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2122662</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾我批中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de0275fa936850113142ab9e58d4f8553ac9627","tid":2122562,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:39:04.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">造謠死全家 !!!!</span></strong></span><br />\n林鄭月娥：疫情倘惡化難保再出招 舉例許多城市禁足令<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538672-20200719.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538672-20200719.htm&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6CrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=400f9a63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538672-20200719.htm&h=b82e7741\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538672-20200719.htm</a>"},{"pid":"02a1537c4241c8fbc840bb7d6169562bb4c23f5e","tid":2122562,"uid":43278,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:40:51.000Z","msg":"要造成恐慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f2c8c47db7e459b2731d2b23c473035c16d1b8","tid":2122562,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"02a1537c4241c8fbc840bb7d6169562bb4c23f5e","tid":2122562,"uid":43278,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:40:51.000Z","msg":"要造成恐慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"一邊澄清一邊散播謠言<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98dd32777bfa1330ebd0b39282c6b78a68ba73d6","tid":2122562,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:47:08.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src